        <ol>
          <li><p>
            Find <m>\gamma(0)</m>.
          </p></li>
          <li><p>
            Determine the length of the curve on <m>t \in [0,4]</m>.
          </p></li>
          <li><p>
            Qualitatively describe the behaviour of the curve as <m>t
            \rightarrow \infty</m>.
          </p></li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </li>
